     = Indonesia_Bogor Regency\n| map_caption         = Location in [[Bogor Regency]]\n}}\n'''Cibinong Station''' is an Indonesian railway station located in Pabuaran, [[Cibinong]], [[Bogor Regency|Bogor]], [[West Java]].\nThe station is located at an altitude of +126 meters, and is included in the Jakarta Operation Area I. Not far from the station (6&nbsp;km) is located an international [[Pakansari Stadium]].\n\n==Schedule==\nHere is the Schedule of KRL Commuter Line at Cibinong Station, based on Gapeka 2017 effective from April 19, 2017.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.krl.co.id/httpwww-krl-co-idwp-contentuploads201703jadwal-gapeka-2017-update-19-april-2017-2-xlsx/|title=Unduh Jadwal Terbaru KRL - Update 19 April 2017|newspaper=KRL|language=id|access-date=2017-05-08}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!No. KA\n!Departures\n!Destinations\n|-\n|1008\n|04.38\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1028\n|06.08\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1505\n|05.22\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1511\n|06.52\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1506\n|08.38\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1621\n|09.17\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1512\n|10.08\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1627\n|10.47\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1622\n|12.43\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1537\n|13.22\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1641\n|13.47\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1628\n|14.13\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1538\n|16.38\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1651\n|17.17\n|[[Angke railway station|Angke]]\n|-\n|1642\n|18.13\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|1657\n|18.47\n|[[Depok railway station|Depok]]\n|-\n|D1 10020\n|19.48\n|[[Nambo railway station|Nambo]]\n|-\n|D1 10019\n|20.50\n|[[Depok railway station|Depok]]\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Bogor Regency]]\n[[Category:Railway stations in West Java]]\n\n{{KCJ Angke - Nambo Line}}\n{{Train Stations in Indonesia|West Java}}\n{{Indone